data.description: Cozy house right in the corner of the street. Renovated Kitchen with new floors on the first floor. Wall AC unit in every room. Big yard that includes enormous trees and a basketball court. Lots of storage room in the garage and workshop, attic converted into a man-cave with skylights. Above the Garage is a in-law apartment which currently has tenants living in it.
data.whatILove: Ready to move in apartment above the garage, a man cave in the attic with sky-views. lots of parking space, big storage shed, peaceful neighborhood. quite area.
